4978628 |accessdate=2020-11-05 |archive-date=2020-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103050358/https://udn.com/news/story/121768/4978628 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，大學學務長與校安中心主任請辭負責<ref name="#11">{{cite news|title=女大生遇害 長榮大學：學務長與校安中心主任請辭負責|date=2020-11-03|work=中央社|url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202011025002.aspx|accessdate=2020-11-05|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119142143/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202011025002.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

